---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ventures | Maple Tyne Technologies" description="As a Venture Studio, we develop a diverse ecosystem of platforms that demonstrate our capacity for end-to-end operational automation.">
	<main class="w-full flex justify-center bg-[var(--surface)] text-[var(--on-surface)]">
		<div class="w-full max-w-[1280px] grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 p-8 min-h-screen">
		  <!-- Header Module -->
		  <div class="col-span-12 border border-[var(--outline)] rounded p-8 mb-8 relative overflow-hidden group">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--surface-container)] to-[var(--surface)] opacity-50 z-0 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
			<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end border-b border-[var(--blueprint-line)] pb-6">
			  <div>
				<span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[var(--surface-container-high)] text-[var(--primary)] border border-[var(--primary)] rounded text-[12px] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-[0.05em] uppercase mb-4 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(118,220,134,0.3)]">
				  [SYS_IDENT_VENTURES]
				</span>
				<h1 class="font-['Geist'] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--data-highlight)] mb-2">
				  Deployed Platforms.
				</h1>
				<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-sm text-[var(--on-surface-variant)] uppercase tracking-wider">
				  End-to-End Operational Automation
				</p>
			  </div>
			</div>
		  </div>

		  <!-- Intro -->
		  <div class="col-span-12 mb-4">
			<p class="font-['Geist'] text-lg text-[var(--on-surface-variant)] max-w-3xl">
			  As a Venture Studio, we develop a diverse ecosystem of platforms that demonstrate our capacity for end-to-end operational automation.
			</p>
		  </div>

		  <!-- Intelligent Energy Orchestration (Flagship) -->
		  <div class="col-span-12 border border-[var(--primary)] rounded p-8 bg-[var(--surface-card)] relative overflow-hidden group shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(118,220,134,0.1)]">
			<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[var(--primary)] opacity-5 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
			<div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
			  <div class="md:col-span-7">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
				  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_8px_var(--primary)]"></span>
				  <span class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-xs text-[var(--primary)] uppercase tracking-widest">[ FLAGSHIP_PROJECT ]</span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="font-['Geist'] text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--data-highlight)] mb-4">
				  Intelligent Energy Orchestration
				</h2>
				<div class="space-y-4 font-['Geist'] text-base text-[var(--on-surface-variant)] leading-relaxed">
				  <p>An AI-native, local-first energy orchestration platform designed to turn standard residential electric vehicles into active financial assets.</p>
				  <p>By autonomously managing bidirectional vehicle-to-home (V2H) energy arbitrage, the system automatically capitalizes on deep electricity tariff differentials.</p>
				  <p>It features true hardware neutrality—communicating seamlessly with multi-vendor hardware—and uses predictive smoothing logic to protect EV battery bounds and prevent rapid cycle wear.</p>
				</div>
			  </div>
			  <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-[var(--blueprint-line)] pt-6 md:pt-0 md:pl-8">
				<div class="space-y-6">
				  <div>
					<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-[10px] text-[var(--outline)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Architecture</p>
					<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-sm text-[var(--data-highlight)]">Local-First / Edge AI</p>
				  </div>
				  <div>
					<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-[10px] text-[var(--outline)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Primary Mechanism</p>
					<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-sm text-[var(--data-highlight)]">V2H Energy Arbitrage</p>
				  </div>
				  <div>
					<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-[10px] text-[var(--outline)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Status</p>
					<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-sm text-[var(--primary)]">[ACTIVE_OPTIMIZATION]</p>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div>
		  </div>

		  <!-- Invoice Generator & EcoAudit Grid -->
		  <div class="col-span-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-2">

			<!-- Invoice Generator -->
			<div class="border border-[var(--outline)] rounded p-8 bg-[var(--surface-card)] hover:border-[var(--secondary)] transition-colors duration-300 flex flex-col">
			  <div class="mb-4">
				<span class="inline-block px-2 py-1 bg-[var(--secondary)]/10 border border-[var(--secondary)]/30 text-[var(--secondary)] rounded text-[10px] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-widest uppercase">
				  [ UTILITY ]
				</span>
			  </div>
			  <h3 class="font-['Geist'] text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--data-highlight)] mb-4">
				Invoice Generator
			  </h3>
			  <p class="font-['Geist'] text-base text-[var(--on-surface-variant)] leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">
				A micro-SaaS platform engineered for high-speed billing and workflow automation. This utility showcases our lightweight deployment strategies and frictionless client-side financial engineering, designed for maximum operational speed.
			  </p>
			  <div class="border-t border-[var(--blueprint-line)] pt-4 mt-auto">
				<p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-xs text-[var(--outline)]">DEPLOYMENT: CLIENT_SIDE</p>
			  </div>
			</div>

			<!-- EcoAudit Canada -->
			<div class="border border-[var(--outline)] rounded p-8 bg-[var(--surface-card)] hover:border-[#F57C00] transition-colors duration-300 flex flex-col">
			  <div class="mb-4">
				<span class="inline-block px-2 py-1 bg-[#F57C00]/10 border border-[#F57C00]/30 text-[#F57C00] rounded text-[10px] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-widest uppercase">
				  [ VENTURE_LAB ]
				</span>
			  </div>
			  <h3 class="font-['Geist'] text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--data-highlight)] mb-4">
				EcoAudit Canada
			  </h3>
			  <p class="font-['Geist'] text-base text-[var(--on-surface-variant)] leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">
				Currently in active development, this compliance-first sustainability analytics platform is automating the future of Canadian carbon auditing.
			  </p>
			  <div class="border-t border-[var(--blueprint-line)] pt-4 mt-auto">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
				  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#F57C00] animate-pulse"></span>
				  <p class="font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-xs text-[#F57C00]">STATUS: IN_DEVELOPMENT</p>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div>

		  </div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
